name: Apexutility
tagline: Formal Concept Analysis and New Similarity Method In c#
body:
### Welcome to GitHub Pages.
My Name is Mohsen Asghari. I have been developing This project for two months, it is based on C# and we are trying to create tools for generating Formal Concept Analysis in order to enhance the similarity accuracy of Cased-based reasoning systems.   

### Designer Templates
This program uses Inclose algorithm, that is available on "https://sourceforge.net/projects/inclose/" SourceForge

### Creating pages manually
This utility is fully open-source and it is created in order to increase similarity and case retrieval in CBR cycle.


### Support or Contact
